snippet.title: Monster Prom: XXL Teaser Trailer (Available for Pre-Purchase NOW on Nintendo Switch!)
snippet.description:
PRE-PURCHASE NOW: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/monster-prom-xxl-switch/
Monster Prom: XXL - the bundled up, content filled edition of Monster Prom is coming to the Nintendo Switch starting May 21st!
